Package org.eclipse.mosaic.fed.application.app.api.os

Interface OperatingSystem

All Known Subinterfaces:
AgentOperatingSystem, ChargingStationOperatingSystem, ElectricVehicleOperatingSystem, RoadSideUnitOperatingSystem, ServerOperatingSystem, TrafficLightOperatingSystem, TrafficManagementCenterOperatingSystem, VehicleOperatingSystem
All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractSimulationUnit, AgentUnit, ChargingStationUnit, ElectricVehicleUnit, RoadSideUnit, ServerUnit, TrafficLightGroupUnit, TrafficManagementCenterUnit, VehicleUnit
public interface OperatingSystem
This interface describes all necessary functionality for units to be simulated.

      default long getSimulationTimeMs()
      Returns the time difference in milliseconds since a well-defined start time - here milliseconds since the simulation start time. 1.1.1970 00:00:00.000 Needs to be aligned with SAE J2735 DF_DDateTime, DF_DTime, DE_DSecond. Unit: [ms].
      Returns:
      the simulation time. Unit: [ms].
